description:
This is the additional puzzle pack for "Jigsaw Masterpieces". The following 10 puzzle images are included.
-Milk chocolate and colorful jelly candies
-Colorful candy popcorn
-Lollipop candies
-Pink Donuts
-Colorful macarons
-Jelly Rolls
-Colored Chocolate Granules
-Colorful sweets on a table
-Colorful ice cream
-Little Lollipop Candies
name: Colorful Sweets 2
